Issue: Account Dropdown Visible Without Login

When a user visits the website without logging in, the account dropdown (Dashboard,
View Profile, Logout) is visible.
Current Behavior:
Non-logged-in users can see Dashboard, View Profile, and Logout. Clicking Logout then
changes it to a Login button.
Expected Behavior:
If the user is not logged in, only the Login button should be displayed. The account
dropdown should appear only after successful login.

